  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare

        -  the non invasive measurement of arterial pressure (CNAP monitor)

        -  with the invasive measurement of arterial pressure (radial artery catheter) during
           induction and maintenance of general anesthesia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    Difficulty to include more patients
  </why_stopped>
